        <mxCell id="sub_scp" value="SCP (この OU だけに追加適用):&#xa;{&quot;Effect&quot;: &quot;Deny&quot;, &quot;Action&quot;: &quot;*&quot;,&#xa; &quot;Condition&quot;: {&quot;StringNotEqualsIfExists&quot;:&#xa;   {&quot;aws:RequestedRegion&quot;: [&quot;ap-northeast-1&quot;]}}}&#xa;&#xa;→ ap-northeast-1 以外での API 呼び出しを拒否" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=9;fontStyle=0;fontColor=#DD344C;" vertex="1" parent="1">
